Once upon a time in a forest there lived a monky on a berry tree which was along the banks of the river.
In the same forest there lived Crocodile and his wife . One day the Crocodile came and rested in the banks of the river. The kind harted monky offered him some food, the Crocodile liked it.
Soon they become friends. One day the monky gave some food for the Crocodile's Wife she liked it. She was jellous as she did not like her husband spend time with the Monky, so she told his husband to bring the Monky's hart.

